<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Specialty: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline>Horserace Game&nbsp;<a href="glossary.php#Horserace_Game" title="Explain this specialty" target="help"><img alt="[?]" style="cursor: help;" src="/graphic/question.gif" border=0></a><br>
